&lt;li&gt;Regularly review and optimize the plan based on sales performance and market dynamics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver monthly bottoms up forecasting and maintain quarterly updates to plan&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Process&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be the primary point of contact for customers as they move through the buying journey: prospect, discovery, demo, quote, pilot, negotiation, and close.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Disciplined execution of prospecting and sales processes, including entering information and data in Salesforce, so that pipeline generation goals are met, forecast accuracy is high, and quota is regularly attained.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the customer relationship for the first year to create / close cross-sell opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understands and executes MEDDICC sales methodology and process, and continually seeks to develop expertise in these areas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
