&lt;li&gt;Serves as the senior escalation point for high-priority, customer-impacting incidents, driving unified communication and fast resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establishes and enforces policies, procedures, and runbooks that ensure a consistent, high-quality technical service experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifies patterns in customer issues and incidents, and leads proactive initiatives to reduce ticket volume and recurrence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
